CONGRESSIONAL PLAN WITH LVP IN MAIN LIVING AREAS; WARM COLORS, GRANITE KITCHEN COUNTERS; 42'' MAPLE CABINETS; STAINLESS APPLIANCES; EXTENDED SCREENED LANAI OVERLOOKING LAKE. HANDICAPPED ACCESSIBLE LIGHT SWITCHES AND OPEN PRIMARY SHOWER; WINDOW TREATMENTS REMAIN. FLEX ROOM OR OFFICE OFF KITCHEN. PAVERS ON FRONT DRIVEWAY AND LANAI; LOCATED ON DEADEND/CUL DE SAC STREET; ACCESS TO CLUBHOUSE WITH BALLROOM, BILLARD ROOM, ARTS AND CRAFTS ROOM, CARD ROOMS, INDOOR AND OUTDOOR POOLS, SAUNA, FITNESS, BOCCE BALL COURTS, HAR-TRU TENNIS COURTS. WITHIN 2 BLOCKS OF IMAX THEATRE AND SLAMMER AND SQUIRE GOLF COURSE IN WORLD GOLF VILLAGE. ACTIVE AND QUIET COMMUNITY!
